Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你光芒普照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的照耀之下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心靈一隅會生出陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法照亮你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1910)}瑪利亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還真是個聰明的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你身邊逃走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個眼神是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻洞穿一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將不加修飾的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真實收入眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不加修飾的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准… 看穿我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼毫不慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她… 她明明失去了大澤瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使故地重遊 我還是沒法殺死亡靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 還是沒能做個了結呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我一起上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我 又會被留在列車裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連同思念 懺悔 後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又會像那天一樣在此失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又將藕斷絲連的留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不去追大澤瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而執著於我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南 我是個說到做到的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞的事 由我想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你可不準死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不想受你保護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你並肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使看不到顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能感受到瑪利亞的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以知道 是因為瑪利亞是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你力量的泉源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你通過尋找新的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,企圖擺脫夏姆的亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞不是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友而戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那份斬不斷 理還亂的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然憑那點心願就解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許你走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要在這裡 由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這個手感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿在毆打白色的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要兩個迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們擁有同一個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 夏姆不會叫我阿爾法魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他只在最後叫過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果沒有目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只為滿足一己私慾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自然會領悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新名字的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}孤獨{\r}」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天就不會重演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就能擺脫夏姆的亡靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你總是現出奇怪的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時像夏姆的咖啡色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天更是純白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆死後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的… 你的心也隨他去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都成了我無可忘卻的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有停滯在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定權在活人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為生者 我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許你再死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許你死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若在這裡無法拯救什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那天還有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實被束縛在那個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我以為 只要造出迦南那個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能接近… 接近夏姆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南早已被解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從夏姆的亡靈中 從不斷重複的那一天中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有同一個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有同樣刺青的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆 你陰魂不散的糾纏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要擺脫「{\1c&H0000FF}蛇{\r}」的詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中指挑這邊 對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是呢 迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多事 要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒法復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒法復原？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經沒法回到過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷口比預想中的淺 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 這裡不是天國？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這麼死氣沉沉的天國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和芸芸說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她拚命把你背來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤 芸芸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實先生 這裡是極樂淨土嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先我們一步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南無阿彌陀佛 南無阿彌陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯 我還活著呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那快救救瑪利亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後… 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給可憐的芸芸上點供品吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,供品最好是饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完飯她恢復精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 芸芸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於迦南 我查了你手機撥過的號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經停機了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起待了那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果對迦南還是一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南眼中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南肩負的重擔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看 想去瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本以為終於可以和她並肩而立了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要體諒她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的願望是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她想保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 還是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論走到何方 迦南都不讓我和她並肩而立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能 你們的境遇差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們可以互相偎依吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相偎依？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 如果只讓心相依的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只讓心相依…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那座灰色的城市裡 只有瑪利亞閃耀著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不是我希望和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞就不會遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 無論身在何方 我都能感受到瑪利亞的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 無論身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕天各一方 我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,產蟹旺季仍遙遙無期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座城市和我們初履之時別無二致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有新聞略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已經沒人感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}新生的空白接連被新的色彩所掩蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊 電話郵件都聯繫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個奇怪事件怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「消失的村莊」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不要提了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我有另一個猛料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼料？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上海 有個男人為某位女性傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苦戀未果 追尋著她的芳蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪門子低級小說啊 認真點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要跳槽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這本低級小說的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須由我來書寫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(400,200)}還活著啊 因為因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 出門也不關電視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那小屁股多翹 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把芸芸的藥給爸爸寄去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說能複製
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了 她本人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工打得太多 來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吧 老兄 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好 差不多該進入下一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}致即將踏入新世界的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}送上奈奈的一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這曲子還真是應景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}敬請欣賞 來自聽眾「絲綢之路饅頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「LIFE」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲綢之路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饅頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充斥著喧囂的洪流 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你過去不是拿「好厲害」當口頭禪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想最近都沒聽到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了站在迦南身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是感歎周圍的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要讓自己變厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家各自努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拚搏著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以熠熠生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實並不是無法企及的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能像實先生所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心心相依吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉 香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吃香蕉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油加香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要道別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准拿商品墊胸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓顧客高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這座城市的種種邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面凝聚著我對紅塵的留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這座城市的所見所聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這座城市的紛紜思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命 如此絢爛奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人無法直視
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 儘管眼睛生疼 我還是正視了她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個普通女孩的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是死性不改 還敢用我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句話原樣奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況這次對手特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨臂的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
